{"tid":55220,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日玩鋤dee比人呃晒d錢，手足倒評下理啦","createTime":"2016-12-26T08:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T10:44:30.000Z","uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58054b4ee4e6e590a94dbbc0270d5d7be32847d3","tid":55220,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:34:33.000Z","msg":"我渣住 <br />\n33356789JQKA2 <br />\n<br />\n屌，佢地係咁出pair 我係咁pass已經火火地 <br />\n<br />\n佢地1個出左5對pair <br />\n1個4對 <br />\n我同另外一個人一隻都冇出過 <br />\n之後個條友忍唔住出pair2大晒之後佢出56789 <br />\n哈，我心諗出五隻仲唔係我復仇 <br />\n不過佢隻9岩岩大過我 <br />\n我咪出JQKA2 <br />\n<br />\n癡線跟住佢地話唔比出 <br />\n又話咩冇JQKA2 <br />\n<br />\n屌 我梗係唔撚信佢， <br />\n不過個陣佢地三條友一人一把口 <br />\n我最後頂唔順話由9得你地啦 <br />\n之後個條友再出AKQJ10 最後階磗4結向左走向右走左 <br />\n仲大大聲串9我話&lsquo;四炒盛惠$5.2&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\n個下我嬲到反台話屌 你玩撚晒啦之後走左 <br />\n到依家都比晒錢同佢地反撚晒面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無錢搭車 行左十個鐘由荃灣行返去觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗諗下都唔知佢地係咪天仙局呃9我錢"},{"pid":"e907d290220b54566514a77a642d67f7191e2bfd","tid":55220,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f8c7fff5de5418152122c43957d1d5e5333992","tid":55220,"uid":49858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/26/163722_52cb7c8c9a3b46578c6a3053c9ece8cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F163722_52cb7c8c9a3b46578c6a3053c9ece8cb.jpg&h=aa15da9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0399417e4fa8317e021c2613dd23b2b452cfa819","tid":55220,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"